headline: Delta Air Lines, Inc. (DAL) Strengthens International Expansion
summary: Delta Air Lines, Inc. (NYSE:DAL) is one of the high-growth, low P/E stocks to buy now. On February 4, the Delta Air Lines, Inc. (NYSE:DAL) board approved a quarterly dividend of $0.1875.
